practices. Applicant believes that the proposed activities will benefit the public by promoting competition, lower
financing costs, and more innovative financing. Applicant also believes that approval of this application will
allow Company to provide a wider range of services and added convenience to its customers. Applicant believes that
the proposed activities will not result in any unsound banking practices or other adverse effects.
In publishing the proposal for comment, the Board does not take a position on issues raised by the proposal. Notice
